class hmkit.autoapi.properties.hmproperty.HmProperty(propbytes=None, id=None, value=None, timestamp=None, failure=None)¶

Bases: bytearray

Represents property block which can include value, timestamp and failure Components. components are represented by component.property_component_value.PropertyComponentValue, component.property_component_timestamp.PropertyComponentTimestamp and component.property_component_failure.PropertyComponentFailure

create_bytes_from_components(identifier)¶

constructs property bytes from different components. [for internal usage]

findcomponents()¶
get_propvalue_bytes()¶

returns the property value component bytes [for internal usage]

get_propvalue_length()¶

returns the property value component length [for internal usage]

getcomponent_valuebytes()¶

returns the component value bytes [for internal usage]

getdata_component()¶

returns the component value class object for PropertyComponentValue [for internal usage]

getfailure_component()¶
getproperty_bytes()¶

returns the property bytes (all the components) [for internal usage]

getproperty_identifier()¶

returns the property Identifier [for internal usage]

gettimestamp()¶

retuns datetime stamp value

gettimestamp_component()¶

returns the component timestamp class object [for internal usage]
